Package: topotpx
Title: Estimation of Topographical Topic Models
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Kushal K. Dey<kkdey@uchicago.edu>
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10),
    slam,
    parallel
Suggests:
    MASS
Description: Posterior maximization for topographical topic models.Such a model finds its applications in phylogenetic dispersion fields and assemblage maps analysis. This is a modification of the `maptpx` package due to
    Matt Taddy. If you want to take advantage of openmp parallelization, uncomment
    the relevant flags in src/MAKEVARS before compiling.
Maintainer: Kushal K. Dey <kkdey@uchicago.edu>
License: GPL-3
URL: http://kkdey.github.io/
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
